# Copy to .env (gitignored) and fill in.

# OpenFIGI — used by Phase 1B VGT N-PORT-P fetcher for CUSIP → ticker
# lookup. Optional: anonymous tier (no key) works but is slow
# (5 req/min × 10 jobs/request). With a free key:
# 250 req/min × 100 jobs/request — ~100x faster.
#
# Register at https://www.openfigi.com/api → "Get an API Key" (free).
OPENFIGI_API_KEY=
